{"tid":123051,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【毒男難題】一個廿四孝母親定又靚又叻又愛你既女友","createTime":"2017-02-16T13:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T03:54:49.000Z","uid":38177,"like":17,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc41f590c036fe5e412e75daa06beffc8d46b1b","tid":123051,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"一個廿四孝媽媽，對你有求必應，夜番會等你，肚餓會煮飯你食，無錢會俾你，會聽你既心事，想學咩都俾你學，唔想番學會幫你請假再關心你，睇你有咩需要<br />\n<br />\n定<br />\n<br />\n一個女神級既女友，有c至d級身材，有錢會俾你洗，唔會介意你無錢，隨傳隨到，滿足你任何性需要，處女，唔識會為你學，千依百順，會聽你講心事，係朋友面前會俾哂面你，私底下有野不高興會坦白講你知，會嗲你，陪你食平野，錫你荷包，得閒俾小驚喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3372f6da8ba6c3773dbc365ebb96351862f312","tid":123051,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"早啲瞓啦朋友"},{"pid":"e1984ecba06e88a5983b7b7385dfa36c68558aee","tid":123051,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早啲瞓啦朋友</blockquote><br />\n答你就答啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e889c984f1198d47427bd01bacee01fc9832ad64","tid":123051,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"要老母既，女朋友會係咩代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84126a9fab4421c886a2f6c81f7a95aa4ebec5f5","tid":123051,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要老母既，女朋友會係咩代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/